1. Noncommercial Use Only. You may use the Software only for Noncommercial Purposes. A “Noncommercial Purpose” is any purpose other than a Commercial Purpose.

2. Commercial Purpose Defined. “Commercial Purpose” means using the Software in a way that is intended for or directed toward commercial advantage or monetary compensation.

3. Explicitly Allowed Use — Internal Training, for education intent and purposes. Notwithstanding the restrictions above, you may use the Software for **internal training of your employees**, including workshops, tutorials, onboarding, or skill development — **provided that such training is not part of a commercial offering**, and does not involve the use of the Software in production, customer-facing systems, or operations that generate revenue.

4. No Other Rights. This license does not grant you any right to sell, sublicense, or offer the Software or any derivative for any form of compensation.

5. No Warranty. THE SOFTWARE IS PROVIDED "AS IS", WITHOUT WARRANTY OF ANY KIND.

6. Required Disclosure of Modifications:
If you make any modifications to the Software for use within your organization (whether for internal training, evaluation, or other Noncommercial Purposes), you must make those modifications publicly available under the same license terms. You may do so by:
